<p>Thailand’s Queen Mother Sirikit, 93, died late on Friday at King Chulalongkorn Memorial Hospital, the royal household announced; she was the wife of the late King Bhumibol Adulyadej and the mother of the current King Vajiralongkorn . Palace statements said she had been hospitalized since 2019 with several ailments and suffered a blood infection this month before her condition worsened . The royal household said the king has ordered a year-long period of mourning; Thai media and broadcasters showed immediate signs of national mourning after the announcement .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/SWwqCQ9DBsWC2Ukexhb5mv6EH4y_1TViTBMRPZP2nAGgHErZqvloenWnOzhAzgrxaNL-DeOzHuGYwCmitQwJm_HKmYSB2lHvoV4e-ps4j5usi2D_JkZcGODCZkoTq_X2fanTJNFvUKmgMQgF0JQwjKLAbJ8xHSqzfEEQvv_Chif6KToyVgypudVddujxe8o' alt='Queen Sirikit of Thailand with King Bhumibol Adulyadej; portraits of the couple have been widely displayed across the country.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Royal development work: Sirikit oversaw projects focused on helping the rural poor, preserving traditional crafts and environmental protection, often acting as patron and supervisor for long-running initiatives</li><li>International image: She traveled widely with King Bhumibol, building diplomatic relationships and cultivating a glamorous public image that drew international magazine coverage</li><li>Domestic reverence: The Thai monarchy is widely venerated and portraits of Sirikit and the late king have been displayed in homes and shops, reflecting the deep cultural role the royal family plays in public life</li></ul><blockquote>I had heard that she had been unwell and, given that she was in her 90s, I knew this day would come, - Sasis Putthasit</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Thai royal household: The palace announced that her condition worsened and that she passed away at Chulalongkorn Hospital, and assigned members of the royal family to begin a year-long mourning period. (<a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/10/25/thailands-queen-mother-sirikit-dead-at-93-palace'>Al Jazeera</a>)</li><li>A grieving household worker (citizen view): A housekeeper said she felt sad because Sirikit &#x27;was a mother figure to the country,&#x27; reflecting personal and popular sorrow among ordinary Thais. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1951148/thailands-former-queen-sirikit-dead-at-93-palace'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>Academic commentator: An academic noted the passing is profoundly significant for the royal family and the nation because of Sirikit&#x27;s popularity and her connection to the late king&#x27;s long, revered reign. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1951148/thailands-former-queen-sirikit-dead-at-93-palace'>Dawn</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2025/10/24/world/asia/queen-sirikit-thailand-dead.html'>Sirikit, Glamorous Former Queen of Thailand Who Wielded Power, Dies at 93</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2025/10/25/thailands-queen-mother-sirikit-dead-at-93-palace'>Thailand mourns as beloved Queen Mother Sirikit dies at 93</a> - aljazeera.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/sirikit-queen-mother-of-thailand-dies-aged-93/a-74492484'>Sirikit, queen mother of Thailand, dies aged 93</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1951148/thailands-former-queen-sirikit-dead-at-93-palace'>Thailand’s former queen Sirikit dead at 93: palace</a> - dawn.com</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cp8ed1ednjdo'>Thailand&#x27;s former queen Sirikit dies aged 93</a> - bbc.com</li><li><a href='https://www.thehindu.com/news/international/thailands-queen-mother-sirikit-has-died-at-age-93/article70200545.ece'>Thailand’s Queen Mother Sirikit has died at age 93</a> - thehindu.com</li><li><a href='https://www.pbs.org/newshour/world/thailands-queen-mother-sirikit-dies-at-age-93'>Thailand’s Queen Mother Sirikit dies at age 93</a> - pbs.org</li><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/Internationa